INT. POSY'S STUDY — EARLY MORNING, DAY 03
Small room. A desk, two chairs. Morning light barely through the curtain.
POSY sits with his tea. Already been awake a while.
VIVOTH closes the door behind him.
Neither of them speaks first.

The man took a long deep breath.

